org.turbogwt.mvp.databind.client.property

Interface PropertyAccessor<T,F>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Model type
    F - Property type
    All Superinterfaces:
    org.turbogwt.core.providers.client.ProvidesValue<T,F>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BooleanPropertyAccessor<T>, DatePropertyAccessor<T>, NumberPropertyAccessor<T>, TextPropertyAccessor<T>

    public interface PropertyAccessor<T,F>
extends org.turbogwt.core.providers.client.ProvidesValue<T,F>
    This interface is meant to provide access to some property of an object. Simply, it should call the getter and setter of a specific property.

    Serves as support for third-party subjects to manage object properties, following the IoC pattern.

    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
    See Also:
    InversionOfControl
